            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-xl-12">
                <p class="fs-5">
                    This project is a REST API for a blog, providing endpoints for manage the blog. It include user authentication, blog posts, comments, and file uploads. It is designed with a focus on security, performance, and scalability.
                </p>
                <h5>Structure of Objects</h5>
                <Strong>User</Strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>name: {first: string, last: string}</li>
                    <li>email: string </li>
                    <li>password: string </li>
                    <li>Role: string</li>
                    <li>Date Joined: Date</li>
                </ul>
                <Strong>Blog</Strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Name: {first: string, last: string}</li>
                    <li>Author: Identifier </li>
                    <li>Date of Update: Date </li>
                    <li>Date of Creation: Date</li>
                </ul>
                <Strong>Post</Strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>title: string</li>
                    <li>content: string </li>
                    <li>Blog: Identifier </li>
                    <li>Last Update: Date </li>
                    <li>Date of Creation: Date</li>
                </ul>
                <Strong>Comment</Strong>
                <ul>
                    
                    <li>content: string </li>
                    <li>Post: Identifier </li>
                    <li>Author: Identifier </li>
                    <li>Date of Creation: Date</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
